# Frontend Design (Impeccable)

Create distinctive, production-grade frontend interfaces that avoid generic "AI slop" aesthetics.

## Design Direction
Commit to a BOLD aesthetic direction with clear purpose, tone, and differentiation.

## Typography
- Choose distinctive fonts. **DON'T**: Inter, Roboto, Arial, Open Sans
- Better: Instrument Sans, Plus Jakarta Sans, Outfit, Onest, Figtree, Fraunces
- Use modular type scale with fluid sizing (clamp)

## Color & Theme
- Use OKLCH for perceptually uniform palettes
- Tint neutrals toward brand hue
- **DON'T**: gray text on colored backgrounds, pure black (#000), AI color palette (cyan-on-dark, purple gradients)

## Layout & Space
- Create visual rhythm through varied spacing
- **DON'T**: wrap everything in cards, nest cards, identical card grids, center everything

## Motion
- Use exponential easing (ease-out-quart/quint/expo)
- Only animate transform and opacity
- **DON'T**: bounce or elastic easing

## Anti-Patterns (AI Slop)
- No glassmorphism everywhere
- No rounded rectangles with generic shadows
- No hero metric layout templates
- No sparklines as decoration
- No modals unless truly necessary

## The Test
If someone says "AI made this" immediately — redesign it.

